title: An ok place
text: We were here a month. The bed and bedding was good. The room was comfortable. The free breakfast did not cater to women and I never got a cup of coffee asking it for 3 times. The first day they forgot my order totally but brought my husbands. The other problem is the rooms are not soundproof. When you walk off property you are on a major interhighway.

title: An excellent place for dinner
text: We came here for dinner and loved the food. The waiter assisted with choosing items and everything we had was delicious. Highly recommend this place

title: The breakfast was delicious
text: We came here for breakfast and was not disappointed. The food variety was excellent and the service was outstanding

title: An excellent place for a snack
text: We went in for a small snack and the food was so great we ate more than we expected too. The chocolates are delicious as well as the savory pastries

title: An excellent place to have a drink and look at the water
text: This was a very comfortable and inviting place to sit and relax. The drinks were good and the service excellent.

title: An excellent experience
text: We came here for relaxation and was not disappointed. The room was comfortable with great bedding and plenty of hot water. The staff was very helpful and went that extra mile to make you feel appreciated.. The restaurants had fantastic food. A place I would go back to again.

title: An excellent budget hotel
text: We stayed here for 2 weeks and enjoyed our visit. The room was comfortable with excellent hot water. The staff was excellent and if you needed anything they accommodated you as quick as possible. The room service was great and the breakfast was excellent. I would highly recommend this place.

title: An excellent experience
text: I was so looking forward to this restaurant and was not disappointed. Each course was delicious and artistically presented. The service was outstanding. Well worth the visit.

title: An excellent tea
text: We came here for high tea and it was wonderful. The variety was outstanding and the service was great. Loved the music during the tea.

title: An excellent place
text: Loved this place. it was a great experience and such a warm giving place. Everyone should come here for a visit

title: A great place
text: We went here because we where told they have the best chicken. We had their crispy chicken, butter chicken and chicken malai tikka. The food was great and they were able to reduce the spice for us. It was good and went back 2 more times.

title: Not a place to visit
text: We went because the reviews were so good. We needed not spicy food but got spicy food. They wanted to sell us fish as fresh and when they showed us it was thawing. The beer was good

title: an ok museum
text: It was a nice museum to see the partitioning off of India and Pakistan. Very informative about how the partitioning came about wish it had been a bit more concise.

title: A great place
text: A must see in Amritsar. It is wonderful and great crowd control. We also took in the meal which was very good.

title: A great place for a brew and pizza
text: Have gone here 3 times. The pizza is good. Enjoyed the beers and was just able to sit and relax. The staff is great and very accommodating. Worth the visit

title: An excellent budget hotel
text: This is an excellent budget hotel. We had a comfortable room and bed. The hotel had an electric kettle, wifi, tv and plenty of hot water. They provided extra blankets and heater. The staff was great. Breakfast was very tasty and they had room service for meals throughout day. They also make reservations for game park. A great find.

title: A good place
text: We went here for the game park but enjoyed the hotel environment as well as the room. The bed was comfortable and well appointed. The staff was good but you had to ask for room to be serviced or items to be replenished. The breakfast was good with eggs cooked to order. The lunch and dinner is buffet style.

title: A good place
text: The hotel is beautiful with a great view of the Taj Lake Palace. Very close to the museum. The room was comfortable and well appointed . The breakfast was good and eggs were cooked to order. I would not recommend the all inclusive and there are other food places in area.

title: An excellent experience
text: This place is beautiful. the room is comfortable and well appointed. We were able to watch the sunset from our room. The food was great and everything was delicious. This was a great experience and would highly recommend it to everyone.

title: More a nature reserve
text: We went on 4 safari's and saw no tigers. We did see other animals so it is more a nature reserve. The jeeps can only enter after sunrise and exit before sunset which makes it difficult to see nocturnal animals such as tigers. You can't pick who takes you and we had one man who parked the jeep most of the time. He took us to gate 20 minutes before time was up and gate was closed. They drove the jeep about a kilometer away and waited for the time to elapse and then drove us back to respect hotels. Would recommend a different park

title: An excellent climb
text: The fort is a nice climb which allows you to see the area from high up. You see natural beauty as well as monkeys. Worth the visit

title: A great experience
text: We stopped here for a rest stop and loved it. It is a charming coffee/tea shop with great crepes. They also serve breakfast and sandwiches. Loved the place and highly recommend

title: The building is impressive
text: The building is vey impressive and a great architectural interest. I found the layout a bit not planned out in which direction they wanted you to go and we wound up having to double back.

title: Loved the geometry of the place
text: A great way to view the stars. It has great open areas and you can take your time musing what people might have seen years ago

title: A very nice place to walk around
text: The landscape is outstanding as well as the architectural structure. It was a great walk and loved the history

title: an excellent budget hotel
text: This is one of the best budget hotels to stay in. The rooms are well appointed. The beds are very comfortable. the staff was accommodating and very helpful. The breakfast was very good. I would highly recommend this place if it meets your travel plans

title: An average experience
text: The restaurant is comfortable. The food was average i did not find anything that stood out. The restaurant has a bakery next to it and if you buy from them you can have it sent to restaurant .

title: An amazing experience
text: We came here for lunch and it was exceptional. The service was great. The food was excellent and made to out specifications. We ate in dining area and they allowed us to have our tea in courtyard. Each area was so great. highly recommend

title: A great place
text: We went there for lunch while site seeing. The staff was very good and helpful. The meal was delicious. It was a great atmosphere and a nice place to sit and ponder what you are seeing. highly recommend a stop

title: A very good place to walk around
text: Loved the building and the collection of textiles and weapons. We bought the total package and If I had to do it again I would only buy for this site

title: Lovely ride
text: We loved the ride when we left Darjeeling. We had left Ghoom and the train broke down. We had to take a cab back as it was going to take an hour to get an engineer out to even look at train

title: A great vantage point
text: This was a great place to go early in the morning to watch the sunrise on the mountain. Well worth the 3:30 wake up

title: A great place
text: We had an excellent experience in this hotel. The room was well appointed with a comfortable bed and great little amenities like a robe. The staff was so accommodating and would help you as soon as possible. The food was great and especially loved the fish pie and roasted chicken. We would go into the sitting room and sit at fireplace and have high tea or drinks. This is a great place and will come back again.

title: An excellent stay while waiting for a train
text: We had a 14 hour lay over and found this hotel. It was clean, had bed and bathroom. There was also a tv. You could order room service and have meals in room. The staff is very accommodating and flexible to people needing to catch trains with long layovers. We got in at 6:00 am and left 9 pm. The staff is awesome

title: A great find
text: This restaurant was very nice. It overlooks the river and was very peaceful. The food was good and able to be made to our dietary needs.

title: A great architectural structure
text: This place is a great architectural structure with a European feeling. The space is corded off so there was no place to say prayers.

title: A great restaurant
text: We were here and the food was amazing. The chef made food to our specifications. All the food was outstanding and the wait staff was great.

title: A great experience
text: We went here and we were a half hour before it opened. The sister's were so kind and let us in because we were leaving. It was a great spiritual experience. Highly recommended

title: A great place
text: We came here and they were wonderful. They made food not spicy for us and everyone here was very helpful . Highly recommend

title: A really great find
text: We found this place and it was a fun place on New Year's Eve. We went back another time. The food was good and the beer was good.

title: a nice archetectual structure
text: The architecture of the building is great. The new building has a museum which was average with limited items

title: A nice place to relax
text: We went here for food and a beer. A great place to sit and unwind. The food was great and was able to get unspicy food which is what we wanted

title: A very pleasant stay
text: We were here for a night and the bed was comfortable with plenty of hot water. The staff was very good and the room was very well appointed. The food was great with the chef making suggestions. Would highly recommend it. My only question is why is there a window between the bedroom and bathroom

title: A great place
text: This hotel is well appointed . The bed is comfortable and there is plenty of hot water. The staff is wonderful from the moment you get in till the time you leave. We stayed 30 days and this place was great. They could not help us enough. The food was great and the chef made food to order. The spa was wonderful. I highly recommend this place.

title: A great visit
text: A really nice palace to walk around the property has a temple as well as nice appointed receiving room.

title: A great restaurant
text: We ate here and found the food very tasty. The chef would make items for our level of spice and heat we could tolerate. All the wait staff was great and would make wonderful suggestions for us. A great restaurant

title: A great restaurant
text: This place was excellent. The chef came out and assessed what foods would be good for our pallet. The staff was very accommodating. Well worth the visit

title: A great place
text: This hotel is off the main road. It has a comfortable bed and hot water. The hotel offers a great breakfast and has a refrigerator in room The staff is wonderful and willing to help. Great laundry serice.

title: A really poor budget hotel
text: The bed is comfortable and in a nice area which is all I can say that is positive. The room is the size of a postage stamp. Very dusty which caused an allergic response. They do not have laundry service unless you have 3 days to wait for its return. Many mosquitoes and we saw a mouse. Room service was to 10 pm but at 9pm told not available. The staff is not helpful and check in was a problem. Find another budget hotel.

title: A wonderful place
text: A great place to walk around with wonderful garden as well as a magnificent architectural building. A must see

title: This museum is awesome
text: I truly loved this museum. It had great fossils and archeological finds from around the world. I found the information on science fascinating.

title: A nice garden
text: The gardens were pretty and the fountains were enjoyable. Went at night and it was lit up. Wished they had seating areas

title: A great church
text: This is a great church are which has gothic architectural structures. I thought the grounds were great

title: A great lunch buffet
text: Came here for lunch and it was great. The staff was very friendly and very helpful. I found a great selection in the buffet.

title: Not bad
text: Being from US found different menu then I am use to but the food choices were good . I found it not bad but not a lot of unspicy choices

title: A great place if you want meat and fish
text: The food was grilled well and also the plates were a generous proportion. There is no alcohol and offered water. Dessert was good

title: not really good
text: We were looking for food and told it was a good place. The food was more a plate of everything mushed together and the food was mediocre.

title: loved seeing the items
text: We were going to go to the Taj Falkhauama and this was some of the items that were in the Palace. I liked how they separated the different art from around the world

title: A nice place for a walk
text: Loved walking around the old fort and seeing the wonderful green areas. a walk to the top is a bit strenuous. My only complaint is that the tour guides don't take no for an answer and you have to yell to get them to walk away from you
